acter, it indicates the position of insertion of the next Content Block, inside a Content Section.\r\n\r\nThe state machine of a basic Content Cursor is shown below.\r\n<img src="https://docs.google.com/drawings/pub?id=1y0G12OT-X9XiEn8KM1HCXttg0fbR0sKQPmEU5rKFmTs&amp;w=960&amp;h=720"/>', 'iOS AppDev Patterns: Content Cursor', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '87-revision-8', '', '', '2011-05-15 22:54:14', '2011-05-16 06:54:14', '', 87, 'http://www.avishek.net/blog/?p=95', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
