main Specific Language if you were so inclined).\r\n', 'Driving data visualisation over a queue using RabbitMQ and lambda-queuer', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '588-revision-4', '', '', '2011-09-17 11:13:16', '2011-09-17 19:13:16', '', 588, 'http://avishek.net/blog/?p=594', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
